graph TD
    Enter([User navigates to Route]) --> IsPublic{Public route?}
    IsPublic -- Yes --> Render[Render Page]
    IsPublic -- No  --> HasJWT{JWT in Auth Context?}

    HasJWT -- No  --> GoLogin[Redirect to /login]
    HasJWT -- Yes --> Expired{Token expired?}

    Expired -- Yes --> Clear[Clear AuthContext] --> GoLogin
    Expired -- No  --> AdminRoute{Requires ADMIN role?}

    AdminRoute -- No  --> HasEnv{Environment scope present?}
    AdminRoute -- Yes --> IsAdmin{User is ADMIN?}

    IsAdmin -- Yes --> Render
    IsAdmin -- No  --> Go403[Redirect to /403 Forbidden]

    HasEnv -- Yes --> Render
    HasEnv -- No  --> Go403
